29:36.024 --> 29:39.444
I could see this world where you're like
a famous Instagramming--

29:39.527 --> 29:42.030
The bartender
with the handlebar mustache.

29:42.113 --> 29:43.615
-See?
-Why not? I love it.

29:43.698 --> 29:45.867
You're ready
to take your new look on.

29:45.950 --> 29:49.245
That's what I like about it.
I'm confident about it.

29:50.413 --> 29:51.498
What do you have here?

29:51.581 --> 29:54.375
-[Antoni] You'll be making dinner...
-I'm gonna make dinner?

29:54.459 --> 29:56.836
-...for your family before your event.
-Okay.

29:56.920 --> 30:00.298
-How are you feeling?
-Compared to when I started this,

30:00.381 --> 30:04.719
a lot better. I feel like the hero
who's at the end of the odyssey.

30:04.803 --> 30:07.347
I love that.
Hero at the end of the odyssey.

30:07.931 --> 30:10.683
We're gonna be making
all'Amatriciana sauce.

30:10.767 --> 30:12.352
So, I got prosciutto.

