32:22.148 --> 32:25.818
Something that isn't saying,
"I wanna get drunk with my mates."

32:25.902 --> 32:28.321
I've also got you shoes.
I love these.

32:28.404 --> 32:31.574
You can wear them with blue,
black, with cream, navy.

32:31.658 --> 32:33.868
There's so many clothes
you can wear with this.

32:33.952 --> 32:37.038
