-Come on through, you handsome bugger.

32:46.464 --> 32:47.840
[all shouting]

32:48.883 --> 32:50.718
-Slick, right?
-[Jonathan] So slick.

32:50.802 --> 32:53.012
Super slim. How do say it? Like rad.

32:53.096 --> 32:54.931
-There you go.
-[Bobby] That looks like a start

32:55.014 --> 32:57.684
-to some cheesy sitcom of the '90s.
-Oh, yeah.

32:57.767 --> 32:59.894
-We have to do it like this.
-Yeah. Hello.

33:00.311 --> 33:03.690
