you deserve it.

34:32.945 --> 34:35.615
-You've been open to all of it.
-Absolutely.

34:35.698 --> 34:39.577
-Bring something positive to the table.
-You have got an event to get ready for.

34:39.660 --> 34:41.204
-Love you.
-Love you, guys.

34:41.287 --> 34:43.164
Enjoy your new home. Have fun tonight.

34:43.247 --> 34:46.209
-Bye, Leo.
-Bye, Leo.

34:46.292 --> 34:47.251
Bye.

