35:49.188 --> 35:50.022
Tongue.

35:50.648 --> 35:53.025
Get your boys. Your boys wanna see you.

35:53.109 --> 35:54.902
-[Leo] Let's go.
-[Bethany gasps]

35:54.986 --> 35:58.698
Oh, my God. It looks so grown-up.

36:00.616 --> 36:03.119
[chuckles] Look at this island.

36:05.163 --> 36:08.040
-I can fit everything in there.
-I know.

36:08.124 --> 36:10.459
Oh, my gosh. It's so great.

36:10.793 --> 36:11.961
Oh, it's not over.

36:12.044 --> 36:13.462
-No? No?
-No.

36:14.463 --> 36:17.258
Oh, my goodness. Oh, my goodness.

36:17.341 --> 36:19.802
What did they do to my room? [chuckles]

36:20.803 --> 36:22.054
[all laughing]

36:22.138 --> 36:25.057
-She literally stopped in her tracks.
-She's like, "Whoa."

36:25.141 --> 36:29.187
-Okay.
-First of all, your side, my side.

36:29.270 --> 36:32.023
-[laughing]
-Yeah, that's right.

36:32.106 --> 36:34.442
-Look at this.
-You have grown-up clothes.

36:34.525 --> 36:36.485
I have, like, clean underwear.

36:36.986 --> 36:40.573
Shows how dirty his underwear was.
