36:40.656 --> 36:45.161
And that's what a gasp she gave,
like, "Clean underwear, wow!"

36:45.244 --> 36:46.537
[laughing]

36:46.996 --> 36:49.749
I've conquered some fears.
I've been in public with people.

36:49.832 --> 36:53.252
I can't wait for tonight.
So far, I'm ready for it, like...

36:53.628 --> 36:56.047
-I'm gonna make you proud.
-I am so proud of you.

36:56.130 --> 36:57.757
I'm already proud of you.

36:58.758 --> 37:01.802
I'm gonna make you fresh pasta
from scratch.

37:01.886 --> 37:03.012
Well, I'm starving.

37:03.596 --> 37:05.306
-Okay. I'll get ready.
-I'll be back.

37:05.389 --> 37:08.100
-I'll let you know when I'm ready.
-Wonderful.

37:11.687 --> 37:12.980
[whistling]

37:13.522 --> 37:16.776
