-[Tan] They do.

38:59.920 --> 39:01.922
He's putting on my favorite blazer.

39:02.006 --> 39:05.176
-[Antoni] Is it purple? Is it a mauve?
-It's got a lilac thread

39:05.259 --> 39:07.219
