39:07.928 --> 39:09.388
-Ta-da!
-[all cheering]

39:09.472 --> 39:11.432
-Hi.
-Yeah.

39:11.515 --> 39:12.975
[groaning]

39:15.644 --> 39:18.314
-He looks confident, which I love.
-Bye-bye.

39:18.397 --> 39:21.817
