40:19.625 --> 40:22.586
I just loved how he's engaging
with other parents.

40:23.129 --> 40:25.339
-[Bethany] I'm so proud of you.
-Okay.

40:25.423 --> 40:29.385
I'm glad you took it to heart.
I see the change, and I love it.

40:29.468 --> 40:30.761
And you look amazing.

40:32.304 --> 40:35.474
I did it for you guys.
This is like step number one.

40:35.558 --> 40:36.392
Yes.

40:36.851 --> 40:39.228
[Tan] I really think
that he's going to shine

40:39.311 --> 40:42.982
and is gonna be able to take onboard
the lessons we've taught him.

40:43.065 --> 40:46.986
[Karamo] Leo now has the confidence
to connect with other parents, his wife,

40:47.069 --> 40:49.155
and know that he's not alone
in this journey.

40:49.238 --> 40:51.615
It's easy to compare yourself
to other people.

40:51.699 --> 40:54.952
At the end of the day,
a dad who provides for his family

40:55.035 --> 40:58.289
